PC Number Date Chapter Bill Dept
 2020-00422020-02-03,  ,  ISED,  , 
ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectChambre de commerce et d'industrie du Sud-Ouest de Montréal (Quebec) ** Change of Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE ET D'INDUSTRIE DU SUD-OUEST DE MONTRÉAL, in Quebec, to CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES of its district from the boroughs of Sud-Ouest, LaSalle, and Verdun to the boroughs of LaSalle, Verdun, Sud-Ouest, Côte-des-Neiges-Notre-Dame-de-Grâce, the portion of the Ville-Marie borough located west of Saint-Laurent Boulevard, including the Quai King-Edward, the Quai Alexandra, the Quai Bickerdike, and the Cité du Havre, the portion of the borough of Lachine/Saint-Pierre lying east of the St-Pierre interchange, north of the Lachine Canal, and north-east of Highway 20, being the territory of the former City of Saint-Pierre, the portion of the Plateau-Mont-Royal borough lying between Sherbrooke Street to the south, Mont-Royal Avenue to the north, Saint-Laurent Boulevard to the east, and Parc and University streets to the west, the cities of Westmount, Côte-Saint-Luc, Montreal West and Hampstead.
RegistrationRegistration: UNR/
